{"type":"message","id":"cc92b9ff","parentId":"b3a5a531","timestamp":"2026-05-24T01:47:39.203Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"2c9a6130ebfb4fb19dda3058c6a84b67","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Composio MCP WhatsApp tools send messages\",\n  \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 749,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8c05d14e07f3ecbc\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhatsapp MCP Integration for AI Agents | Composio\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8c05d14e07f3ecbc\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://composio.dev/toolkits/whatsapp\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3d7160060d7973b0\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhatsapp MCP for AI Agents Securely connect your AI agents and chatbots (Claude, ChatGPT, Cursor, etc) with Whatsapp MCP or direct API to send messages , fetch conversations, automate replies, and manage contacts through natural language.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3d7160060d7973b0\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"composio.dev\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6a303835c062cf71\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhatsapp Automation (Grade A) - Claude Skill | Skills Directory\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6a303835c062cf71\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.skillsdirectory.com/skills/composiohq-whatsapp-automation\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a2145bdfe3e4ccb6\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSecurity-tested tools skill for Claude AI. Grade A. Automate WhatsApp Business tasks via Rube MCP ( Composio ): send messages , manage templates, upload media, and handle contacts. Always search tools first for current schemas.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a2145bdfe3e4ccb6\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.skillsdirectory.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"85ae30f8e3d60500\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhatsApp MCP Guide: Connect WhatsApp with AI & Automation Tools ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"85ae30f8e3d60500\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://app.wasenderapi.com/blog/whatsapp-mcp-the-ultimate-guide-to-ai-automation-integration\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"44b5e2e6b453b81e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhat is WhatsApp MCP ? WhatsApp MCP (Model Context Protocol) is a standardized way to connect WhatsApp APIs with AI agents and automation tools . It allows external systems to interact with WhatsApp features such as sending messages , managing contacts, and handling groups through structured commands.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"44b5e2e6b453b81e\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"app.wasenderapi.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a3b1e421389dc272\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGitHub - lharries/whatsapp-mcp: WhatsApp MCP server\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a3b1e421389dc272\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/lharries/whatsapp-mcp\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f9bb4c796ff5e055\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThis is a Model Context Protocol ( MCP ) server for WhatsApp . With this you can search and read your personal Whatsapp messages (including images, videos, documents, and audio messages ), search your contacts and send messages to either individuals or groups. You can also send media files including images, videos, documents, and audio messages .\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f9bb4c796ff5e055\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"github.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0106a1d9d786edfa\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow to Use WhatsApp MCP Server: A Complete Guide\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0106a1d9d786edfa\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://dev.to/furudo_erika_7633eee4afa5/how-to-use-whatsapp-mcp-server-a-complete-guide-172m\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a8ae7cd680e43262\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIntroduction Model Context Protocol ( MCP ) has emerged as a powerful way to extend AI capabilities by providing standardized methods for applications to access external tools and services. When combined with messaging platforms like WhatsApp , MCP servers can transform how businesses and developers interact with customers, automating responses while maintaining access to real-time data and ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a8ae7cd680e43262\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"dev.to\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"Composio MCP WhatsApp tools send messages","provider":"duckduckgo","count":5,"tookMs":749,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"duckduckgo","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8c05d14e07f3ecbc\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWhatsapp MCP Integration for AI Agents | Composio\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8c05d14e07f3ecbc\">>>","url":"https://composio.dev/toolkits/whatsapp","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3d7160060d7973b0\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWhatsapp MCP for AI Agents Securely connect your AI agents and chatbots (Claude, ChatGPT, Cursor, etc) with Whatsapp MCP or direct API to send messages , fetch conversations, automate replies, and manage contacts through natural language.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3d7160060d7973b0\">>>","siteName":"composio.dev"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"6a303835c062cf71\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWhatsapp Automation (Grade A) - Claude Skill | Skills Directory\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"6a