ing images, videos, documents, and audio messages .\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f9bb4c796ff5e055\">>>","siteName":"github.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0106a1d9d786edfa\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHow to Use WhatsApp MCP Server: A Complete Guide\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0106a1d9d786edfa\">>>","url":"https://dev.to/furudo_erika_7633eee4afa5/how-to-use-whatsapp-mcp-server-a-complete-guide-172m","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a8ae7cd680e43262\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nIntroduction Model Context Protocol ( MCP ) has emerged as a powerful way to extend AI capabilities by providing standardized methods for applications to access external tools and services. When combined with messaging platforms like WhatsApp , MCP servers can transform how businesses and developers interact with customers, automating responses while maintaining access to real-time data and ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a8ae7cd680e43262\">>>","siteName":"dev.to"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779587259085}}
